y-wisdom-al-hikmah","tag-dates-al-tamr","tag-drink-al-sharab","tag-fasting-al-siyam","tag-food-al-taam","tag-manners-adab","tag-sunnah","tag-water-al-maa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3Va","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":3738,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/20\/iftar-dates-water\/","url_meta":{"origin":15076,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Iftar: Breaking fast with dates and water","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you breaks his fast, let him break it with dates for they are blessed. If they are not found, let him break it with water for it is pure.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40542,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/04\/even-smallest-blessings\/","url_meta":{"origin":15076,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: Allah asks about even the smallest blessings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, among the blessing you will be questioned about on the Day of Resurrection are the cool shade, fresh dates, and cold water.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2369 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10106,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/01\/prophet-gives-everything-he-has\/","url_meta":{"origin":15076,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Charity: The Prophet gives everything he has each night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe house of Muhammad has not reached evening with a share of dates or grain.\" In another narration, Anas said, \"The Prophet would not store anything for tomorrow.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1215 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25653,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/20\/wipe-non-leather-socks-sandals\/","url_meta":{"origin":15076,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Wiping over non-leather socks, sandals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 20, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mughirah ibn Shu\u2019bah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, performed ablution by wiping over non-leather socks and sandals. Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cIt is the view of more than one of the scholars, as is said by Sufyan al-Thawri, Ibn al-Mubarak, Al-Shafi\u2019i, Ahmad, and Ishaq. They said one may\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15329,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/allah-displeased-if-no-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":15076,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Allah displeased with unmindful gatherings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo people sit in a gathering without remembering Allah, or sending blessings upon their Prophet, but that they will earn the displeasure of Allah. If Allah wills, He will punish them. If He wills, He will forgive them.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13714,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/24\/sea-water-pure-halal\/","url_meta":{"origin":15076,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Water: Sea water is pure, animals halal to eat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked about sea water and he said, \u201cIts water is purifying for ablution,\u00a0and its dead animals are lawful to eat.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"It is the opinion of most of the jurists among the companions of the Prophet, peace\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15076","targetHints":{"